  "subject": "Create SW Upgrade Blueprint",
  "commit_message": "Create SW Upgrade Blueprint\n\nUAT: Add support to multiple responses for a single request\n\n     Set property IN_UAT=1 during UAT execution\n     so blueprints can tune their settings to values more\n     suitable for testing (like timeouts)\n\n     Added 'times' field to specify expected number of invocations\n\n     Add a UAT blueprint for PNF SW Upgrade UC\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-2091\nChange-Id: I062a135347efa5bc8520bdc6c9e9b79bf46dcac4\nSigned-off-by: gummar <raj.gumma@est.tech>\n",
